OL,6,FHe was diagnosed with bowel cancer in
OL,7,F2022, which spread to his liver, and
OL,8,Fthe county announced his death on
OL,9,FSunday, December 28, 2025.
OL,11,FDan Cherry, who succeeded Morris as
OL,12,FGlamorgan's chief executive two years
OL,13,Fago, said: "Everyone here at Glamorgan
OL,14,FCounty Cricket Club and further afield
OL,15,Fare devastated on hearing the awful
OL,16,Fnews about Hugh.
