OL,6,F"The club, Welsh cricket and the game
OL,7,Fas a whole has lost a great player, a
OL,8,Ftireless administrator, and a fine
OL,9,Fhuman being of great dignity and
OL,10,Fintegrity."
OL,12,FMorris, who overcame throat cancer
OL,13,Fafter his diagnosis in 2002, was a
OL,14,Fpatron of Heads Up, a charity which
OL,15,Ffocuses on head and neck cancer, and
OL,16,Fhelped to raise #300,000 over an eight-
OL,17,Fyear period.
OL,19,FHe was awarded an MBE in 2022 for
OL,20,Fservices to cricket and charity.
